The paper deals with the recognition and characterization of a specific type of graph, namely map graphs, which are a generalization of planar graphs. This falls under the category of discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The paper also involves the study of the structure of bipartite graphs and their incidence graphs, which are topics in computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.DS, cs.GT). The efficient recognition algorithm mentioned in the abstract suggests that the paper may also involve computational complexity (cs.CC).
